{"tid":2362710,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"張六常見字入嚟","createTime":"2021-01-11T15:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T18:37:06.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"debc95f21a842c2255001147f2e0f48bc831bfaf","tid":2362710,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:40:22.000Z","msg":"你間u開左微博<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你有幻想过在这样一个北欧学院派的大学念书吗？<br />\n自1477年起，为追求知识而存在的地方，<br />\n坐落在一个可以骑自行车自由通行的大小刚好的城市，维京古都，<br />\n宿舍旁就是小森林，<br />\n13个学生nation任你选择&mdash;&mdash;从早餐到晚餐，图书馆奖学金代代相传的宿舍楼，还有好玩的趴体，8位诺奖校友，学术排名全球前100。<br />\n<br />\nHej 大家好呀，今天是industrial analytics的思远来分享自己专业的课程安排啦 这个是我们专业的课程链接 网页链接<br />\n我这个项目理论上是两年120学分的，有两个方向，一个是工业工程(ie）方向，一个是计算机(cs）方向。在最终毕业之后也会根据选课和毕设来判定拿的是IE的毕业证还是CS的毕业<br />\n<br />\n嗨大家好！这里是绯叶君[兔子] 给大家分享一下圣诞节时我们自己DIY的瑞典传统圣诞餐Julbord![haha]<br />\n<br />\n「开餐」Gl&ouml;gg 圣诞热红酒<br />\n「Plate 1」Seafood<br />\n「Plate 2」Christmas ham<br />\n「Plate 3」Warm dishes<br />\n「Plate 4」Cheese<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://weibo.com/3363681224/JC741qccS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F3363681224%2FJC741qccS&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=dc0e20c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://weibo.com/3363681224/JC741qccS</a>"},{"pid":"55940682e5ccca39b69c8dd18a2b77a254c7367d","tid":2362710,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"Uppsala University 2021 ranking<br />\nQS 124<br />\nTimes 111<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f130bd5d9a43d595faca5a364bc484e0faf303","tid":2362710,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我隨口 up 下大學名，唔好咁認真否則會